prepare white rice 

shred finely
 - 150 g cabbage 
 - 1 medium carrot
season with
 - 4 tsp  rice wine vinegar 
set aside 
add to sauté pan
olive oil
 - 30 g minced ginger
 - 2 minced garlic cloves 
cook 2 minutes
add
 - 500 g lean ground pork 
cook until almost done
stir in
 - 60g hoisin sauce
 - 30g soy sauce 
 - 1 tsp sesame oil
 - 1/4 tsp white pepper
 - 1/4 tsp chinese five spice 
 - pinch msg
set aside 
add cabbage to pan 
cover
cook 5 minutes 
serve in bowls
garnish with
 - chili crisp sauce
 - fried shallots
 - fried wonton strips
 - plum sauce 
 - sesame seeds


